OL,3,CFamily 'devastated' after losing
OL,4,Ceverything in house fire days before
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FITV News' Grace Pascoe spoke to Dan
OL,8,FHughes about his family's loss.
OL,10,FA family have said they are
OL,11,F"devastated" after a fire tore through
OL,12,Ftheir home, destroying all of their
OL,13,Fbelongings including presents for
OL,14,Ftheir daughters, just days before
OL,15,FChristmas.
OL,17,FFirefighters were called to the blaze
OL,18,Fin Goonhavern, near Newquay, Cornwall
OL,19,Fat around 10.30pm on Saturday 14
OL,20,FDecember.
