OL,7,FThe cause of the fire is being
OL,8,Finvestigated, Cornwall Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService said.
OL,11,FDan Hughes said his wife, Asher, was
OL,12,Fin the living room when she saw smoke
OL,13,Fcoming from the kitchen and evacuated
OL,14,Fthe property. He added that within 10
OL,15,Fminutes the whole house was alight.
