OL,3,CFamily 'devastated' after losing
OL,4,Ceverything in house fire days before
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"You see stories of house fires, and
OL,8,Fyou think that's never going to happen
OL,9,Fto me. At the time when it happened, I
OL,10,Fthink there was so much adrenaline it
OL,11,Fhadn't actually set in. We were just
OL,12,Fstanding and watching. There was
OL,13,Fnothing more that we could do," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FMr Hughes, who shares the house with
OL,17,Fhis wife and two daughters, Bella,
OL,18,Fseven, and Daisy, one, has lived in
OL,19,Fthe property for the past seven years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
