OL,3,CFamily 'devastated' after losing
OL,4,Ceverything in house fire days before
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FHe said they'd built the house up over
OL,8,Ftime, but now they'd lost everything.
OL,10,F"I went to work in these clothes and
OL,11,FI've still got them on, because
OL,12,Feverything else is in there. It's our
OL,13,Flivelihood really - everything we've
OL,14,Fever owned and worked for. I feel
OL,15,Fempty now," he said.
OL,17,FHe added they've also lost the
OL,18,Fpresents they were planning to give
OL,19,Ftheir daughters for Christmas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
