OL,3,CFamily 'devastated' after losing
OL,4,Ceverything in house fire days before
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"My wife makes 99% of the clothes that
OL,8,Four daughters wear and that's all
OL,9,Finside as well. She's lost all of her
OL,10,Fsewing stuff, all the Christmas
OL,11,Fclothes she's made. It's devastating.
OL,12,FProper devastating."
OL,14,FA GoFundMe page has been set up online
OL,15,Fby a friend, and Mr Hughes said he has
OL,16,Fbeen "overwhelmed" by support.
