OL,3,CFamily 'devastated' after losing
OL,4,Ceverything in house fire days before
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"Knowing how happy people are to
OL,8,Fcontribute makes us feel very cared
OL,9,Ffor. My phone has been going off non-
OL,10,Fstop. I've had so many messages and I
OL,11,Fjust can't reply to everyone."
OL,13,FHe added: "We've got to be positive
OL,14,Freally, just so our daughters are
OL,15,Fstill happy and try and do Christmas
OL,16,Fas normal.
OL,18,F"As difficult as it will be, we've
OL,19,Fstill got to get up and keep going. We
OL,20,Fcan't just mope around, we've got to
OL,21,Fkeep going."
